      <title>苹果准备在国际上销售 Vision Pro</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-14/apple-prepares-to-sell-mixed-reality-headset-vision-pro-internationally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，苹果公司正准备开始在美国以外的市场销售混合现实耳机 Vision Pro。马克·古尔曼 (Mark Gurman) 在彭博电视上报道称，Vision Pro 将虚拟内容与用户周围的现实世界视图混合在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-14/apple-prepares-to-sell-mixed-reality-headset-vision-pro-internationally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 将以 9.5 亿美元收购 Delivery Hero 台湾业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/uber-eats-to-buy-foodpanda-taiwan-business-from-delivery-hero</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Uber Technologies Inc. 将以 9.5 亿美元收购 Delivery Hero SE 在台湾的 Foodpanda 业务，以巩固其对亚洲这一重要市场的控制，同时寻求在该地区的扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/uber-eats-to-buy-foodpanda-taiwan-business-from-delivery-hero</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Square Enix 股价因前景疲软而跌幅为 13 年来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/square-enix-shares-tumble-by-most-in-13-years-on-weak-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Square Enix Holdings Co. 总裁表示，近期大制作游戏的销量令人失望，而且最近的重组需要数年时间才能取得成果，该公司股价重挫 16%，创 13 年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/square-enix-shares-tumble-by-most-in-13-years-on-weak-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:07:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
