      <title>随着中国科技财报的开始，腾讯的回购计划成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/tencent-s-buyback-plan-in-focus-as-china-tech-earnings-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着腾讯股价反弹，投资者将密切关注周二公布的收益回购计划。]]></description>
